{
  "texts": [
    "The University of Florida (UF) is actively integrating AI into its curriculum and creating avenues for student involvement in designated areas of AI literacy, irrespective of their academic discipline (Southworth et al., 2023, p. 1).",
    "Based on existing data, there is no significant difference between male and female groups in text comprehension.",
    "However, the differences between men and women appear to be most pronounced in SMT_Content and SMT_Style, with women having slightly higher averages.",
    "In addition, ChatGPT was significantly better at reprocessing text than students based on the measured aspects.",
    "ChatGPT outperforms almost every aspect of the assessment."
  ]
}